<p>The easiest way to add Grunt and gruntplugins to an existing <code class="highlighter-rouge">package.json</code> is with the command <code class="highlighter-rouge">npm install &lt;module&gt; --save-dev</code>. Not only will this install <code class="highlighter-rouge">&lt;module&gt;</code> locally, but it will automatically be added to the devDependencies section, using a tilde version range.</p>

<p>For example, this will install the latest version of Grunt in your project folder, adding it to your devDependencies:</p>

<p>Grunt</p>
